<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>
			{% block title %}Gestion de la Mairie - Notification
			{% endblock %}
		</title>
		<style>:root
		{
			--primary-color: #e28743;
			--secondary-color: #eab676;
			--background-color: #eeeee4;
			--text-color: #1D1D1D;
		}

		* {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}

		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: var(--background-color);
			color: var(--text-color);
			padding: 20px;
		}

		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: auto;
			background: white;
			padding: 20px;
			border-radius: 12px;
			box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		.header {
			text-align: center;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
			color: white;
			padding: 20px 0;
		}

		.logo {
			width: 120px;
			height: auto;
			margin-bottom: 16px;
		}

		.content {
			padding: 32px 24px;
		}

		.button {
			display: inline-block;
			background-color: var(--primary-color);
			color: white;
			padding: 14px 32px;
			text-decoration: none;
			border-radius: 8px;
			font-weight: 600;
			transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
		}

		.button:hover {
			background-color: var(--secondary-color);
		}

		.footer {
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 14px;
			color: var(--text-color);
			margin-top: 20px;
			padding: 20px;
			border-top: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
		}

		.footer p {
			color: var(--text-color);
		}

		@media(max-width: 600px) {
			.container {
				margin: 0 10px;
				padding: 10px;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="header">
			<img src="https://glotissement.kaolackcommune.sn/logo.png" alt="Logo Mairie" class="logo">
			<h1>
				{% block header_title %}{% endblock %}
			</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="content"> {% block content %}{% endblock %}
			</div>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>Cordialement,<br>L'équipe de la Mairie</p>
				<p>
					<small>©
						{{ "now"|date('Y') }}
						Mairie - Tous droits réservés</small>
				</p>
				<p>
					<small>Pour toute assistance, contactez notre support :
						{{ get_telephone() }}
					</small>

				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
